{"tid":769984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「鳩嗚團」日收$800？團友求屈穎妍幫追「欠薪」！","createTime":"2018-08-06T15:41:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T05:55:57.000Z","uid":51183,"like":83,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b86baf238c195cf1ce1feadbbaa89e8b30b8a0a2","tid":769984,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T15:41:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180806/58530111\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180806%2F58530111&d=xdIU%2BrzGFHX3CxxFNyih5AhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=aa3ac0fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180806%2F58530111&h=36d2c6fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180806/58530111</a><br />\n<br />\n自從佔旺於2014年清場，時任行政長官梁振英呼籲市民到旺角區消費後，「鳩嗚團」一直響應長期於旺角行人專用區「鳩嗚」，至今已經1,349日。今日10多名團員由菜街轉移陣地到勞工處示威，不滿有「反佔中旗手」之稱的屈穎妍在專欄指，鳩嗚團員日薪有300至800元不等；一方面又向勞工處「求助」，要求勞工處向屈穎妍查詢資料，協助團員找出自己的「幕後金主」。<br />\n<br />\n鳩鳴常客錢寶芬稱，每天在旺角爭取真普選的鳩嗚團友都是完全自發，沒有收取任何資助，是「有汗出、冇糧出」。錢又指，鳩鳴團員在旺角已有1,349日，如若屈穎妍所稱日薪800元計算，收入肯定已超過100萬港元，因此期望勞工處向屈穎妍索取資料，協助鳩嗚團員「追討欠薪」，並要求在處方在14日內回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180806/large/1533544353_c85d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180806%2Flarge%2F1533544353_c85d.jpg&h=003c5175&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鳩嗚團要求勞工署向屈穎妍查詢資料，協助團員找出自己的「幕後金主」。林社炳攝<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180806/large/1533552688_0223.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180806%2Flarge%2F1533552688_0223.jpg&h=7a433e5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n錢寶芬指，如若屈穎妍所稱，團員的累計收入肯定已超過100萬港元。夏家朗攝<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180806/large/1533552687_6eec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180806%2Flarge%2F1533552687_6eec.jpg&h=ad5b6365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屈穎妍快啲提供資料啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36cb3cc3506baed70e75c3f88bacb0a00ca2b880","tid":769984,"uid":25260,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T15:47:32.000Z","msg":"難分真與假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cba8e9dd278451c99998968130199795f1ea39f","tid":769984,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T15:51:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a563cfeb6a5fe7aa7c11a45ce68bdb816855016","tid":769984,"uid":177590,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T15:53:48.000Z","msg":"識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193b0cafc48a183e6c711b9b95fbcfe140cc4bdd","tid":769984,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:12:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 識玩"},{"pid":"4c529201363f319a1f28a0dbd0bea646ae393ef6","tid":769984,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:16:55.000Z","msg":"電視有冇報？"},{"pid":"02ed3c440ba4e967f1ed83584041b7cb5affa5bf","tid":769984,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:18:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21f070ea060907af113639a4c981c52d8101f6f","tid":769984,"uid":27151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:19:39.000Z","msg":"笑撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgm